### 核销券订单接口测试
### 基础配置
@baseUrl = https://grain.griffithres.top
@token = da5f4209-bbb6-4232-87e1-ba8dcf09e323

### 1. 创建订单 - 正常流程
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/wanlshop/voucher/order/create
Content-Type: application/json
token: {{token}}

{
  "goods_id": 1,
  "quantity": 2
}

### 2. 创建订单 - 商品不存在
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/wanlshop/voucher/order/create
Content-Type: application/json
token: {{token}}

{
  "goods_id": 99999,
  "quantity": 1
}

